  "texts": [
    "To further enable transparent and automated incentive mechanisms, Karim et al. [133] explore the integration of AI agents with blockchain, showing how smart contracts and decentralized ledgers facilitate agentto-agent payments, reputation, and governance.",
    "b) Penalty Mechanism Design.",
    "Effective penalty mechanisms can deter free-riding and malicious behaviors by imposing costs (e.g., token deductions or reputation losses) on agents that fail to complete tasks such as missing deadlines or generating lowquality or hallucinated responses [2].",
    "Key penalty approaches include: • Game-theoretic Penalties.",
    "Leveraging principles from game theory, several incentive-compatible penalty schemes have developed to align individual agent behavior with system-wide objectives."
  ]
